  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You launch a set of thrown weapons wrapped in Battle Wire at an enemy, intended to use them as a much more lethal bola. Target an enemy within range, make a ranged Taijutsu attack. On a hit the target takes [weapons damage] + 4d6. </p><p>The target then must make a Dexterity saving thrown, being restrained on a failure and no effects on a successful save. A creature who begins its turn restrained by this jutsu gains 2 ranks of bleeding. A creature can remake the save at the end of their turns.</p>",
